snippet.title: Amber Heard: Aquaman Interview | A superhero who happens to be a woman | Extra Butter
snippet.description:
Amber Heard talks about her role of Mera in the new "Aquaman" movie. Amber tells Mark S. Allen about why it is important to have a superhero who is a woman and discusses the #MeToo movement. #Aquaman

Watch Extra Butter every Friday morning at 9:30 a.m. on ABC10.
